'''Odette Nyiramilimo''' (yavutse 1956) ni [[Rwanda]] umuganga na Senateri. Yabaye umunyamabanga wa Leta ushinzwe imibereho myiza muri guverinoma ya [[Paul Kagame]] kuva muri Werurwe 2000 kugeza Ukwakira 2003<ref>https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/tea/news/east-africa/survivors-rusesabagina-was-no-hero-hotel-rwanda-film--1934890</ref>.

== Amavu n'amavuko ==
Nyiramilimo, [[Abatutsi|umututsi wo mu]] bwoko, yavukiye i Kinunu, [[Umujyi wa Rubavu|perefegitura ya Gisenyi]] mu 1956. Afite imyaka cumi nirindwi mubana ba se cumi n'umunani, yabyawe numugore we wa kabiri.<ref>https://www.bikeforafrica.be/rwanda-2020</ref>

