== Ubuzima bwite ==
Ku myaka itatu, abantu benshi bo mu muryango we baguye mu ntambara yo gushaka ubutegetsi nyuma y'ubwigenge. Nyuma yubwana bwabaye, burimo no kwirukanwa mwishuri kuko yari umututsi<ref>https://peoplepill.com/people/odette-nyiramilimo</ref>,

Nyuma yaje gushyingiranwa na Jean-Baptiste Gasasira, na we wari umuganga, maze nyuma baza gushinga ubuvuzi bwihariye bwo kubyara no kuvura abana i [[Kigali]] buzwi nka ''Le Bon Samaritain'' (" Umusamariya Mwiza ")<ref>https://vymaps.com/RW/Clinique-Leave-Bon-Samartain-Gasasira-Hospital-29690/</ref>

. Nyiramilimo yari umwe mu banyarwanda bagera ku 1.000 bahungiye muri Hotel des Mille Collines mu gihe cya jenoside yo mu 1994 <ref name=":0" /> .

Amateka yubuzima bwe yanditswe muburebure mu gitabo cya Philip Gourevitch ''Turashaka kukumenyesha ko Ejo tuzicwa na Familie yacu''<ref>https://www.thecitizen.co.tz/tanzania/news/africa/survivors-rusesabagina-was-no-hero-as-shown-in-hotel-rwanda-film-2716004</ref>

